MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2007-2254. In re Carson.

Stark App. No. 2007CA00070, 2007-Ohio-5687. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Stark County. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to dismiss and appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the motion to dismiss is denied and the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
